One comes with great restrictions and the other with great costs and risks. We knew how to take the best of both without the downsides. The second was putting together the dream team—an Oceans 11 of sorts. Having worked with one another over the course of 15 years in various capacities and on various projects, we knew that if we started our own company we could embrace common key values and build a work environment that we (and hopefully others) would want to spend most of our waking hours in. Description: Suggesty is an Operator of application intended for women's fashion.

Full Description: Flickering through my phone on the bed before sleep became a routine and a ritual ages ago. Finding myself waking up hugging my phone is a norm these days. Suggesty was born in this mist of my separation anxiety with my phone. One hot summer night in the middle of frantic tapping and scrolling I found talking to myself: "I need a secretary who should organize this in a little neat form." Technology gave online shopping malls freedom and high speed wireless bandwidth made the world too vast giving me endless meaningless choices. I remembered my impulse buys from a beautiful model photo smiling at me or from a time ticking flash sales only to end in countless disappointments.   At some point too much freedom and choices became a source of stress in my online shopping experience. And I thought: "They need an expert"   A year later, they came up with a caring fashion expert genie who considered my preference, my physical appearance, my whereabouts and recommended only the best out fit customized for me. And after wishing it very hard, they managed to put the genie in a bottle called Suggesty and made it into an app for you.

Description: Ecommerce and logistics for seafood
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: i love blue sea works at the intersection of seafood, software, and logistics.  Their ecommerce platform enables consumers to transact directly with seafood producers.  This creates transparency by shortening the supply chain, allowing producers to earn more margin and consumers to get the highest quality products.  Their logistics software allows producers to easily manage orders from any sales channel and includes access to discounted packaging and shipping. The first online sustainable seafood market, ilovebluesea.com is actively growing to become the first national fish market. Seafood currently ships from eight different coastal locations with plans to expand to fifty by end of 2013.  Active partnerships include Seafood Watch and SeaWeb.

Description: MCC specializes in signal analyzers and interface solutions for small area networks.
Full Description: MCC specializes in signal analyzers and interface solutions for small area networks. These networks (electronic signal pathways) provide chip-to-chip communication links in a wide variety of consumer, computer, network, fiberoptic, aerospace, military, and medical electronic circuits. They provide solutions for engineers working with established and emerging integrated circuit communication standards, including I2C Bus (Inter-Integrated Circuit Bus), circuit monitoring and control, power systems, smart batteries, and more.
